Question: In at least one image there are a total of twelve white golf balls.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: http://s3files.core77.com/blog/images/2013/07/golfball-history-05.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many white golf balls are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many white golf balls are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} + {ANSWER1} == 12')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
